      "title": "Sara Sidner",
      "score": 0.04085257362456567,
      "text": "Sara Sidner\nSara Sidner (born May 31, 1972) is an American journalist. She is a correspondent for CNN and CNN International based in Jerusalem starting August 2012, formerly in New Delhi. She currently works in CNN's Los Angeles bureau.",
